			<h1>Welcome To our Website </h1><br />
		<P> <font style="text-align:justify">	Hospital is a committed & specialized ear, nose & throat centre setup by Dr Anil K Monga, an E.N.T. surgeon with 30 yrs experience. Our focus is microsurgery of the ear including surgery for improvement of hearing, cochlear implants & endoscopic sinus surgery. Comprehensive management for sleep apnea & snoring, vertigo & voice disorders is available. Facilities for laser surgery are available. We have a good speech, audiology & hearing aid centre. The centre has 2 fully equipped operation theatres with state of the art equipment like operating microscope, 3 chip cameras, microdebrider.

The hospital is conveniently located on the main road next to Model Town Metro Station (Yellow Line). The hospital is recognized by Directorate of Health Services, Delhi Government.

Dr. Anil K. Monga has done MS (ENT) from G.S. MEDICAL COLLEGE & KEM HOSPITAL, MUMBAI and trained in ear surgery in Germany & USA. He is a Senior Consultant in the Department Of ENT, Sir Ganga Ram Hospital. He has been in ENT practice for 30 yrs. Inspite of his hectic schedule he finds time to conduct workshops & is actively involved with holding free ENT camps in collaboration with social organizations. He has held the office of President of A.O.I. Delhi, 2010-11.<BR /><br />

Our Aim: To provide state of the art surgical facilities in a comfortable, personalized & non intimidating environment.</P><br /></font>
